t-to-return-to-us-7891706%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranya%20Rao's%20Firm%20Had%20Huge%20Land%20Grant%3A%20Congress's%20Tit-For-Tat%20Allegation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor%20Ranya%20Rao%2C%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20smuggling%2014%20kg%20gold%20at%20the%20Bengaluru%20airport%2C%20was%20the%20majority%20shareholder%20of%20a%20company%20that%20received%20a%20massive%20parcel%20of%20government%20land%20during%20the%20BJP%20rule%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20Congress%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20allotment%20was%20facilitated%20by%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20smuggling%20case%20acquired%20political%20overtones%20today%20as%20the%20BJP%20alleged%20the%20actor's%20links%20with%20Congress%20leaders.%20The%20party%20alleged%20that%20since%20her%20arrest%2C%20she%20approached%20two%20ministers%20in%20the%20Siddaramaiah-led%20Congress%20government%20to%20escape%20the%20legal%20net.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20allegations%20came%20shortly%20after.%20Leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20alleged%20that%20under%20the%20Basavaraj%20Bommai-led%20BJP%20government%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20Industrial%20Area%20Development%20Board%20allotted%2012%20acres%20of%20land%20to%20the%20firm%20in%202023%20to%20set%20up%20a%20steel%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20is%20one%20of%20the%20directors%20of%20some%20company%20and%20it%20had%20gone%20through%20legal%20channels.%20The%20land%20audit%20committee%20was%20there%20and%20cleared%20it.%20The%20final%20proceedings%20were%20done%20under%20the%20industry%20minister%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bommai%20told%20reporters%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20at%20state%20level%2C%20single%20window%20agencies%20are%20not%20handled%20by%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20it%20in%20good%20faith.%20We%20want%20industry%20and%20it%20is%20about%20100%20km%20away%20from%20Bengaluru.%20And%20it%20is%20a%20backward%20area.%20To%20develop%20that%20area%2C%20we%20have%20formed%20an%20industrial%20estate...%20How%20can%20we%20know%20that%20some%20director%20in%20that%20company%20will%20do%20illegal%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanya%20Rao%20is%20a%20director%20in%20Xiroda%20India%20Private%20Limited.%20The%20company%20was%20given%2012%20acres%20of%20government%20land%20in%20Shira%20Industrial%20Area%20near%20Tumkuru%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20approval%20was%20granted%20on%20January%202%2C%202023.%20Documents%20show%20that%20the%20land%20allotment%20was%20approved%20in%20the%20137th%20State%20Level%20Single%20Window%20Clearance%20Committee%20(SLSWCC)%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurugesh%20Nirani%2C%20then%20Industries%20Minister%2C%20who%20was%20also%20the%20chairman%20of%20KIADB%2C%20said%20the%20allotment%20was%20made%20after%20a%20green%20light%20from%20the%20committee%20headed%20by%20the%20Industry%20Secretary.%20Thereafter%2C%20%26quot%3B30%20senior%20officials%20discussed%20every%20aspect%20of%20this%20allotment%20and%20after%20this%20it%20was%20allotted%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20process%2C%20no%20illegal%20work%20was%20done%20by%20me%20or%20the%20officials%20as%20the%20Industry%20Minister.%20No%20one%20was%20favoured.%20Whatever%20decision%20was%20taken%2C%20was%20according%20to%20the%20law.%20If%20anyone%20needs%20any%20clarification%2C%20I%20am%20ready%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20BJP%20allegations%20that%20Ranya%20Rao%20contacted%20two%20ministers%2C%20state%20Home%20Minister%20G%20Parameshwara%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%20this%20has%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20CBI.%20Let%20the%20CBI%20come%20out%20with%20their%20findings.%20Till%20then%2C%20this%20is%20speculation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Arrest%20and%20After%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanya%20Rao%20was%20arrested%20last%20Monday%20at%20the%20Bengaluru%20airport%2C%20while%20allegedly%20carrying%2014%20kg%20of%20gold.%20She%20had%20come%20under%20the%20lens%20of%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20due%20to%20her%20frequent%20foreign%20trips.%C2%A0Within%20the%20last%20six%20months%2C%20she%20had%20made%2027%20trips%20to%20Dubai%2C%20and%20also%20the%20United%20States.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20search%20of%20her%20home%20in%20Bengaluru's%20Lavelle%20Road%20yielded%20gold%20jewelry%20worth%20Rs.%202.06%20crore%20and%20Indian%20currency%20amounting%20to%20Rs.%202.67%20crore%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DRI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%2C%20stepdaughter%20of%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20officer%20Ramachandra%20Rao%2C%20was%20produced%20in%20court%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bverbally%20tortured%20and%20threatened%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)'s%20custody%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Btraumatised%20and%20emotionally%20broken%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%2C%20however%2C%20ruled%20out%20physical%20torture%20amid%20speculation%20that%20surfaced%20after%20an%20image%20of%20her%20with%20swollen%20eyes%20and%20bruises%20was%20widely%20circulated%20on%20social%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20judicial%20custody%20till%20March%2024%20but%20hearing%20on%20her%20bail%20application%20is%20scheduled%20for%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741607280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fo22ggpso_ranya-rao_625x300_07_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Franya-raos-firm-had-huge-land-grant-congresss-tit-for-tat-allegation-7891684%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Actor%20Ranya%20Rao%2C%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20smuggling%2014%20kg%20gold%20at%20the%20Bengaluru%20airport%2C%20was%20the%20majority%20shareholder%20of%20a%20company%20that%20received%20a%20massive%20parcel%20of%20government%20land%20during%20the%20BJP%20rule%20in%20