k%5C%22%3Ewidely%20seen%20as%20the%20best%20fit%2C%20even%20better%20than%20the%20F-16%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20designed%20with%20a%20fight%20against%20Russia%20in%20mind.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20it%20can%20take%20off%20from%20civilian%20roads%20and%20is%20easier%20to%20maintain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustin%20Bronk%2C%20a%20leading%20airpower%20expert%20at%20RUSI%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bon%20a%20platform%20level%2C%20the%20Swedish%20Griffin%20would%20be%20a%20better%20fit%20for%20Ukraine's%20requirements%20on%20almost%20every%20level%2C%20just%20platform%20to%20platform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20none%20of%20those%20jets%20have%20so%20far%20been%20committed%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEurope%20also%20has%20other%20jets%2C%20like%20the%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%2C%20but%20those%20haven't%20been%20committed%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20front%20half%20of%20a%20Swedish%20Air%20Force%20Saab%20JAS%2039%20Gripen%20jetfighter%20in%20the%20air.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6718d61801ea6d83dee35ba1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221286%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Swedish%20Air%20Force%20Saab%20JAS%2039%20Gripen%20taking%20part%20in%20a%20NATO%20exercise.%3Cp%3EJOHN%20THYS%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff2db6c5-5a76-4289-82a6-7daa00487e05%5C%22%3ESet%20up%20for%20F-16s%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20major%20problem%20facing%20Ukraine%20is%20that%20its%20program%20is%20heavily%20geared%20toward%20F-16s%2C%20and%20switching%20to%20another%20jet%20type%20would%20cause%20plenty%20of%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20last%20month%20if%20Sweden%20was%20considering%20giving%20it%20Gripens%2C%20P%C3%A5l%20Jonson%2C%20Sweden's%20defense%20minister%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bhaving%20a%20dialogue%26quot%3B%20with%20Ukraine%20and%20other%20countries%20in%20the%20Air%20Force%20Coalition%2C%20a%20group%20of%20allies%20committed%20to%20helping%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Bmore%20challenging%20for%20the%20Ukrainians%20to%20absorb%20another%20fighter%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20Sweden%20was%20being%20advised%20to%20focus%20on%20sending%20airborne%20sensors%20that%20can%20provide%20command%20and%20control%20for%20the%20F-16s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20F-16%20fighter%20jets%20fly%20over%20a%20Patriot%20Air%20and%20Missile%20Defense%20System%20against%20a%20gray%20sky%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67065c9d198738e3a70f4756%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EF-16s%20fly%20over%20a%20Patriot%20Air%20and%20Missile%20Defense%20System%20in%20an%20undisclosed%20location%20in%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FEfrem%20Lukatsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBronk%20said%20the%20Gripen%20could%20serve%20Ukraine%20just%20as%20well%2C%20or%20better%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20so%20much%20that%20goes%20and%20has%20gone%20into%20so%20far%20getting%20the%20F-16s%20up%20and%20running%20in%20terms%20of%20training%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20pilots%2C%20but%20maintainers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20getting%20all%20the%20logistics%20set%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Byou%20couldn't%20just%20swap%20them%20out%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIssues%20with%20training%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-needs-more-trained-pilots-to-maximize-f-16-success-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20created%20a%20bottleneck%20in%20getting%20the%20jets%20into%20the%20air%20over%20Ukraine%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20changing%20to%20a%20new%20type%20would%20create%20a%20whole%20new%20host%20of%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Cancian%2C%20a%20defense%20expert%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%2C%20said%20that%20with%20new%20jets%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20major%20constraint%20is%20pilots%2C%20and%20you%20can't%20just%20rustle%20those%20up%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20important%20thing%20isn't%20so%20much%20the%20differences%20between%20F-16s%20and%20European%20jets%2C%20but%20the%20%26quot%3Btimeline%20and%20numbers%20and%20costs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20another%20problem%20related%20to%20European%20aircraft%3A%20there%20are%20far%20fewer%20of%20each%20compared%20to%20the%20F-16.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20one%20of%20the%20main%20reasons%20the%20F-16%20was%20seen%20as%20the%20best%20fit%20for%20Ukraine%3A%20there%20are%20lots%20of%20them%2C%20as%20well%20as%20plenty%20of%20spare%20parts%20and%20people%20qualified%20to%20work%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Barros%2C%20a%20Russia%20expert%20at%20the%20Institute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War%2C%20called%20the%20F-16%20%26quot%3Bsort%20of%20the%20ideal%20model%20because%20of%20how%20versatile%20and%20universal%20the%20system%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20Europe%20could%20not%20train%20as%20many%20pilots%20on%20aircraft%20like%20the%20Gripen%20because%20%26quot%3Brelatively%20fewer%20countries%26quot%3B%20operate%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEurope%20has%20vowed%20to%20keep%20supporting%20Ukraine%2C%20but%20losing%20US%20help%20requires%20a%20big%20increase%20in%20spending%2C%20and%20some%20weapons%20will%20be%20much%20harder%20to%20replace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20jet%20type%20may%20be%20an%20option%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20if%20the%20F-16%20is%20no%20longer%20available%2C%20but%20it's%20an%20option%20that%20comes%20with%20problems%20Ukraine%20can%20ill%20afford.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-putting-ukraine-f16-fleet-risk-europe-difficult-replace-russia-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A174160647900