%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFather's%20State%3F%26quot%3B%3A%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20As%20MLA%20Asks%20Muslims%20To%20Stay%20Home%20On%20Holi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Bihar%20MLA's%20statement%20asking%20Muslims%20not%20to%20step%20out%20on%20Holi%20has%20drawn%20a%20sharp%20retort%20from%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20who%20has%20asked%20if%20the%20state%20belongs%20to%20the%20MLA's%20father%20and%20dared%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20to%20rebuke%20the%20MLA%20and%20make%20him%20apologise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20his%20remark%2C%20Haribhushan%20Thakur%20Bachol%2C%20MLA%20from%20Bisfi%20in%20Madhubani%20district%2C%20told%20the%20media%20that%20Muslims%20must%20stay%20at%20home%20on%20Holi%20to%20avoid%20a%20confrontation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20Holi%20is%20on%20Friday%20(March%2014)%20and%20Muslims%20hold%20community%20prayers%20on%20Fridays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHoli%20comes%20once%20a%20year.%20It%20is%20a%20festival%20of%20colours.%20Muslim%20friends%20get%20upset%20if%20someone%20puts%20colours%20on%20them.%20That's%20why%20I%20have%20said%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20large%20heart%2C%20then%20step%20out.%20Otherwise%2C%20stay%20at%20home%20so%20there%20is%20no%20confrontation.%20Jumma%20(Friday)%20comes%2052%20times%20a%20year.%20They%20talk%20about%20ganga-jamuna%20culture%20and%20brotherhood.%20Leave%20one%20jumma%20for%20Hindus%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20Opposition%20RJD's%20response%20to%20his%20remarks%2C%20the%20legislator%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Opposition%20wants%20conflict%20so%20that%20their%20vote%20bank%20grows.%20We%20don't%20do%20vote%20bank%20politics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20MLA's%20remarks%2C%20RJD's%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20MLA%20has%20asked%20Muslim%20brothers%20not%20to%20step%20out.%20Is%20this%20father's%20state%3F%20Who%20is%20he%3F%20How%20can%20he%20make%20such%20a%20statement%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20unconscious.%20When%20Dalit%20women%20talk%20about%20their%20rights%20and%20honour%2C%20he%20scolds%20them.%20Does%20he%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20scold%20him%20(MLA)%3F%20JDU%20is%20now%20coloured%20in%20the%20hue%20of%20BJP%20and%20Sangh%20Parivar.%20And%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20cares%20about%20nothing%20other%20than%20his%20chair.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20what%20does%20this%20MLA%20know%3F%20This%20is%20Bihar.%20Five%20Hindus%20will%20protect%20each%20Muslim%20here.%20You%20want%20to%20engineer%20riots.%20But%20whether%20or%20not%20we%20are%20in%20power%2C%20as%20long%20as%20our%20party%20is%20here%2C%20we%20won't%20let%20their%20agenda%20succeed.%20Mr%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20if%20you%20have%20guts%2C%20get%20this%20MLA%20to%20apologise%20in%20the%20Assembly.%20But%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20do%20it.%20The%20country%20is%20watching.%20During%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20row%2C%20he%20called%20Lalu%20Yadav%20%26quot%3Bcourageous%26quot%3B.%20You%20must%20have%20learnt%20something%20from%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav's%20barbs%20at%20Nitish%20Kumar%20come%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20heated%20exchanges%20between%20the%20two%20leaders%20months%20ahead%20of%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20debate%20on%20Governor%20Arif%20Mohammed%20Khan's%20address%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20thundered%20at%20the%20RJD%20leader%20and%20said%20he%20made%20Lalu%20Yadav%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20%26quot%3BEven%20the%20people%20of%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20caste%20(Yadav)%20had%20refused%20to%20make%20him%20CM%2C%20but%20I%20supported%20him.%20I%20made%20your%20father%20(Lalu%20Yadav)%20CM%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%2C%20a%20key%20face%20of%20Janata%20Dal%20p