eed%20not%20learn%20three%20languages%20while%20students%20from%20the%20north%20learn%20only%20one.%20We%20are%20not%20against%20Hindi...%20if%20students%20want%20to%20learn...%20they%20are%20free%20to%20do%20so%20but%20it%20should%20not%20be%20compulsory...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Maran%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Hindi%20Imposition'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20over%20'Hindi%20imposition'%20-%20a%20sensitive%20topic%20in%20the%20south%2C%20and%20particularly%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20where%20violent%20'anti-Hindi'%20riots%20broke%20out%20in%20the%201960s%20and%20which%20has%20always%20been%20opposed%20to%20the%20language%20being%20foisted%20on%20it%20-%20has%20re-erupted%20with%20the%20BJP%20pushing%20its%20new%20education%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftamil-nadu-all-party-meet-hindi-imposition-delimitation-india-into-hindia-kamal-haasan-7853235%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BTrying%20To%20Turn%20India%20Into%20'%3Cem%3EHindia%3C%2Fem%3E'%3F%26quot%3B%20Kamal%20Haasan%20Echoes%20Stalin's%202019%20Jab%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20argues%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20flourished%20with%20a%20two-language%20system%20(Tamil%20and%20English)%20and%20sees%20no%20need%20for%20a%20third.%20The%20BJP%20maintains%20its%20formula%20will%20benefit%20people%20travelling%20to%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%20last%20month%2C%20Mr%20Pradhan%20accused%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20of%20creating%20a%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20narrative%26quot%3B%20and%C2%A0depriving%20students%20of%20academic%20progress%20for%20their%20own%20political%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdharmendra-pradhan-national-education-policy-tamil-nadu-bjp-dmk-ndtv-exclusive-creating-anti-delhi-narrative-education-minister-hits-back-at-mk-stalin-7763064%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BCreating%20Anti-Delhi%20Narrative%26quot%3B%3A%20Education%20Minister%20Slams%20MK%20Stalin%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%20Mr%20Stalin%20and%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20exchanged%20jabs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20claimed%20the%20centre%20had%20done%20more%20for%20Tamil%20speakers%20than%20the%20state%20party%2C%20pointing%20to%20a%20decision%20to%20allow%20candidates%20for%20the%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Force%20entrance%20test%20to%20write%20in%20their%20mother%20tongue.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20urge%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20take%20steps%20towards%20introducing%20the%20curriculum%20of%20medical%20and%20engineering%20courses%20in%20Tamil%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%2C%20however%2C%20to%20note%20the%20centre%20approved%20the%20conduct%20of%20CAPF%20exams%20in%2013%20regional%20languages%2C%20in%202023%2C%20days%20after%20Mr%20Stalin%20protested%20the%20decision%20to%20conduct%20it%20only%20in%20Hindi%20and%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmk-stalins-lkg-student-lecturing-phd-holder-charge-amit-shahs-counter-7867465%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E('Hindi%20imposition')%20is%20like%20an%20kindergarten%20student%20lecturing%20a%20PhD%20holder%3C%2Fa%3E....%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHistory%20is%20clear.%20Those%20who%20tried%20to%20impose%20Hindi%20on%20Tamil%20Nadu%20have%20either%20been%20defeated%20or%20later%20changed%20their%20stance%20and%20aligned%20with%20DMK%20(the%20unspoken%20reference%20was%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20was%20in%20power%20at%20the%20centre%20during%20the%20anti-Hindi%20riots%20of%20the%201960s%20and%20is%20now%20a%20firm%20ally).%20Tamil%20Nadu%20will%20not%20tolerate%20Hindi%20colonialism%20replacing%20Bri