20ladder%2C%20eventually%20reaching%20leadership%20in%20my%20finance%20company.%20But%20I%20never%20felt%20fully%20financially%20secure%2C%20especially%20seeing%20firsthand%20how%20tumultuous%20the%20market%20can%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228ce837ee-3459-417a-86a2-0ba1de8e2791%5C%22%3EI%20started%20selling%20millions%20worth%20of%20sports%20cards%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20while%2C%20I%20was%20still%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-pokemon-renaissance-dethroned-baseball-cards-trading-psa-grading-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuying%20trading%20cards%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20I%20had%20more%20than%20half%20a%20million%20of%20them.%20I%20rented%20a%20storage%20unit%20to%20keep%20them%20all.%20In%202022%2C%20I%20relocated%20from%20New%20York%20City%20to%20Atlanta%20for%20my%20finance%20job.%20I%20had%20my%20dream%20house%20and%20decided%20to%20bring%20my%20cards%20home.%20They%20filled%20almost%20my%20basement%2C%20so%20my%20wife%2C%20Dori%2C%20suggested%20it%20was%20time%20to%20sell%20some.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20oldest%20son%2C%20Joe%20Jr.%2C%20was%2010%20at%20the%20time.%20He%20was%20excited%20by%20the%20idea%2C%20so%20we%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-earn-money-reselling-items-on-ebay-whatnot-poshmark-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eselling%20cards%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20eventually%20on%20WhatNot%2C%20a%20livestreaming%20marketplace.%20At%20first%2C%20we%20were%20filming%20in%20the%20basement%20boiler%20room%3B%20the%20show%20would%20end%20when%20my%20phone%20battery%20died.%20As%20we%20sold%20more%2C%20we%20moved%20to%20my%20younger%20son's%20train%20table%20and%20eventually%20to%20the%20Ping-Pong%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20we%20outgrew%20that%2C%20and%20I%20could%20justify%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-parents-can-improve-wfh-setup-when-office-in-bedroom-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econverting%20a%20bedroom%20into%20a%20home%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20selling%20cards.%20Last%20year%2C%20my%20company%20did%20more%20than%20%245%20million%20in%20sales%20on%20WhatNot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22691e3fdc-1ab8-45d5-84bf-8d56425928ff%5C%22%3EI%20take%20each%20of%20my%20kids%20on%20individual%20trips%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20like%20to%20talk%20about%20my%20personal%20wealth%20or%20net%20worth.%20But%20it's%20clear%20my%20three%20children%2C%20who%20are%20now%2013%2C%2010%2C%20and%206%2C%20are%20growing%20up%20very%20differently%20than%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20like%20to%20travel%20as%20a%20family%2C%20including%20a%20recent%20Thanksgiving%20trip%20to%20the%20Bahamas.%20Dori%20and%20I%20also%20do%20smaller%20trips%20with%20just%20one%20of%20our%20children%20at%20a%20time.%20We're%20preparing%20to%20take%20Joe%20Jr.%20to%20Disney%20%E2%80%94%20he's%20never%20been%2C%20and%20neither%20have%20I.%20This%20past%20fall%2C%20we%20took%20our%20daughter%20to%20New%20York%20City%20and%20did%20everything%20she%20wanted%2C%20including%20seeing%20the%20Rockettes.%20Our%20youngest%20wanted%20to%20eat%20grilled%20cheese%20on%20the%20beach%2C%20so%20we%20took%20him%20to%20Turks%20and%20Caicos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20my%20success%2C%20I%20can%20spend%20quality%20time%20with%20each%20of%20my%20kids.%20That%20makes%20up%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20my%20quantity%20of%20time%20is%20sometimes%20limited%20since%20I%20stream%20for%2024%20hours%20each%20Friday%20through%20Saturday.%20I%20still%20reserve%20Sundays%20for%20faith%20and%20family%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b3d4748c-e350-446b-864c-db0705821dbd%5C%22%3EI%20want%20my%20kids%20to%20have%20resources%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20want%20my%20children%20to%20have%20access%20to%20every%20resource%20they%20need%20to%20succeed.%20Joe%20Jr.%20loves%20basketball%2C%20so%20I%20pay%20for%20every%20basketball%20team%20or%20clinic%20he%20asks%20for.%20Whether%20it's%20dance%20lessons%20or%20tutoring%2C%20I'm%20willing%20to%20spend%20on%20it.%20I%20want%20my%20kids%20to%20work%20for%20their%20success%2C%20but%20I'll%20be%20right%20at%20their%20side%20as%20they%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20the%20differences%20resources%20can%20make.%20My%20mom%20didn't%20have%20money%20but%20wanted%20me%20to%20attend%20a%20private%20high%20school.%20She%20asked%20my%20grandmother%20to%20pay%20for%20my%20schooling%3B%20in%20exchange%2C%20my%20mom%20didn't%20get%20anything%20in%20the%20will%20when%20my%20grandmother%20died%20since%20the%20tuition%20was%20her%20inheritance.%20I'm%20lucky%20not%20to%20have%20to%20make%20difficult%20choices%20like%20that%2C%20but%20I'm%20motivated%20to%20give%20everything%20I%20can%20to%20my%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20anything%2C%20I%20want%20my%20children%20to%20grow%20up%20in%20a%20positive%2C%20encouraging%20environment.%20They'll%20need%20to%20work%20hard%20and%20be%20leaders%2C%20but%20I%20want%20them%20to%20know%20life%20isn't%20just%20about%20making%20money%3B%20it's%20about%20being%20a%20good%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fselling-trading-sports-cards-made-me-a-millionaire-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741605181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cb1d0569253ccddf989880%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fselling-trading-sports-cards-made-me-a-millionaire-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Joe%20DePasquale%20is%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BJoe%20Hollywood%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20app%20WhatNot.%20There%20he%20sells%20sports%20trading%20cards%20for%20which%20he%20made%20over%20%245%20million%20in%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kelly%20Burch)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A77%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fselling-trading-sports-cards-made-me-a-millionaire-2025-3