s%20southeast%20of%20the%20Solomon%20Islands%2C%20northeast%20of%20New%20Caledonia%2C%20and%20west%20of%20Fiji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20archipelago%20consists%20of%20approximately%2083%20islands%20stretching%20650%20km%20in%20a%20Y-shaped%20configuration.%20Port%20Vila%2C%20situated%20on%20Efate%20Island%2C%20serves%20as%20the%20capital%20and%20largest%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormerly%20administered%20jointly%20by%20Britain%20and%20France%2C%20Vanuatu%20gained%20independence%20in%201980.%20Its%20economy%20depends%20on%20tourism%2C%20agriculture%20(copra%2C%20beef%2C%20kava%2C%20cocoa)%2C%20and%20offshore%20financial%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20Vanuatu%20a%20Tax%20Haven%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20Vanuatu%20is%20considered%20a%20tax%20haven.%20The%20nation%20imposes%20no%20income%20tax%2C%20withholding%20tax%2C%20capital%20gains%20tax%2C%20inheritance%20tax%2C%20or%20exchange%20controls%2C%20making%20it%20attractive%20for%20offshore%20financial%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20status%20has%20drawn%20scrutiny%20from%20international%20regulators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Pentecost%20Island%20in%20Vanuatu%2C%20villagers%20perform%20a%20daring%20tradition%20called%20land%20diving%20-%20jumping%20headfirst%20from%20wooden%20towers%20with%20vines%20tied%20to%20their%20ankles.%20Just%20like%20this%20risky%20plunge%2C%20Vanuatu%20faces%20an%20uncertain%20future%20as%20the%20world%20cracks%20down%20on%20tax%20havens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country's%20offshore%20finance%20industry%20took%20off%20in%20the%201970s%20amid%20global%20deregulation.%20But%20as%20financial%20crime%20-%20including%20money%20laundering%2C%20drug%20trafficking%2C%20and%20arms%20smuggling%20-%20became%20rampant%2C%20Vanuatu%20came%20under%20increasing%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Financial%20Action%20Task%20Force%20(FATF)%20placed%20it%20on%20its%20%26quot%3Bgrey%20list%26quot%3B%20for%20weak%20anti-money%20laundering%20regulations%2C%20isolating%20its%20banking%20sector.%20The%202017%20'Paradise%20Papers'%20leak%20exposed%20hidden%20wealth%20tied%20to%20its%20offshore%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVanuatu%20on%20Being%20Labelled%20a%20Tax%20Haven%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVanuatu%20changed%20its%20laws%20to%20improve%20financial%20oversight%20and%20transparency%2C%20leading%20many%20offshore%20banks%20to%20shut%20down.%20Yet%2C%20some%20in%20Vanuatu%20feel%20the%20country%20is%20still%20unfairly%20seen%20as%20a%20tax%20haven.%20Marie%20Noelle%20Ferrieux-Patterson%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20corruption%20watchdog%20'Transparency%20International'%2C%20argues%20that%20some%20US%20states%20offer%20even%20more%20secrecy%20than%20Vanuatu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Global%20Financial%20Crisis%2C%2083%20countries%20agreed%20to%20stricter%20tax%20rules%20under%20the%20Organisation%20for%20Economic%20Cooperation%20and%20Development%20(OECD).%20While%20six%20Pacific%20nations%20joined%2C%20Vanuatu%20remains%20on%20a%20list%20of%20countries%20yet%20to%20take%20full%20action.%20It%20will%20undergo%20an%20OECD%20review%20next%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fnews%2F2010-07-07%2Fvanuatu-upset-by-tax-haven-label%2F895928%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabc.net.au%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Ferrieux-Patterson%20insists%20Vanuatu%20is%20already%20quite%20transparent%2C%20as%20most%20of%20its%20international%20banks%20are%20linked%20to%20Australia%20and%20follow%20both%20Vanuatu%20and%20Australian%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVanuatu's%20History%20with%20Financial%20Controversies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVanuatu's%20reputation%20as%20a%20tax%20haven%20is%20not%20new.%20In%202001%2C%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Barak%20Sope%20was%20charged%20with%20forgery%20over%20unauthorised%20financial%20guarantees%20worth%20between%20%2423%20million%20and%20%24100%20million%20to%20Indian%20businessman%20Amarendra%20Nath%20Ghosh%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2001%2FBUSINESS%2Fasia%2F11%2F13%2Fvanuatu.sope.biz%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20guarantees%2C%20signed%20without%20proper%20approval%2C%20led%20to%20Mr%20Sope's%20removal%20from%20office%20in%20April%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20successor%2C%20Edward%20Natapei%2C%20launched%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20scandal%2C%20while%20Mr%20Sope%2C%20previously%20flagged%20by%20the%20Ombudsman%20Commission%2C%20continued%20to%20face%20legal%20trouble.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Vanuatu's%20financial%20practices%20were%20under%20heightened%20scrutiny%2C%20leading%20to%20its%20withdrawal%20from%20WTO%20accession%20talks%20due%20to%20financial%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741604160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2F8g0q28jo_lalit-modi_625x300_17_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-about-vanuatu-island-nation-that-cancelled-lalit-modis-passport-7891072%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Vanuatu%20government%20cancelled%20the%20passport%20issued%20to%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20founder%20Lalit%20Modi%2C%20saying%20that%20escaping%20extradition%20was%20not%20a%20legitimate%20reason%20for%20citizenship%20in%20the%20island%20nation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-about-vanuatu-island-nation-that-cancelled-lalit-modis-passport-7891072%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20Budget%202025%3A%20New%20airport%2C%20job%20generation%2C%20road%20development%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741604149000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fbudget%2Fnews%2Fmaharashtra-budget-2025-ajit-pawa