oints%20to%20use.%20I%20started%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fchase-ink-business-cash-credit-card-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInk%20Business%20Cash%3C%2Fa%3E%20card%2C%20hit%20the%20welcome%20spend%20amount%2C%20and%20received%20the%20intro%20offer%20bonus%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20I%20started%20the%20process%20again%20with%20the%20next%20card%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fchase-ink-business-unlimited-credit-card-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInk%20Business%20Unlimited%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Once%20I%20hit%20the%20welcome%20bonus%20amount%2C%20those%20points%20were%20deposited%20into%20my%20Chase%20account.%20I%20accumulated%20over%20200%2C000%20miles%20relatively%20quickly%2C%20including%20points%20from%20the%20initial%20welcome%20offer%20bonus%20and%20the%20points%20I%20got%20from%20using%20the%20card%20for%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a1bb2bc3-f4d2-437a-9e71-5ab1e4259351%5C%22%3E2.%20I%20transferred%20all%20my%20points%20to%20one%20card%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20had%20a%20stockpile%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fguide-earning-using-chase-ultimate-rewards-points%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChase%20Ultimate%20Rewards%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%AE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20points%2C%20I%20had%20to%20transfer%20my%20business%20card%20points%20so%20that%20all%20my%20points%20were%20accessible%20from%20one%20card.%20I%20transferred%20my%20points%20to%20my%20Chase%20Sapphire%20Preferred%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fchase-sapphire-preferred-card-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChase%20Sapphire%20Preferred%3C%2Fa%3E%20account%20already%20had%20roughly%20125%2C000%20points%20from%20a%20previous%20welcome%20offer%20and%20additional%20accumulation%20that%20had%20yet%20to%20be%20used.%20Although%20we%20didn't%20use%20this%20option%2C%20you%20can%20also%20transfer%20points%20from%20a%20household%20member's%20Chase%20credit%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223a0fa4d6-51f2-4017-a0a0-880d86a19b22%5C%22%3E3.%20I%20set%20an%20alert%20to%20get%20the%20cheapest%20tickets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20piece%20of%20the%20puzzle%20was%20to%20find%20affordable%20tickets%20for%20which%20we%20had%20enough%20points.%20I%20set%20a%20price%20alert%20on%20Google%20Flights%20for%20the%20days%20we%20were%20interested%20in%2C%20and%20then%20waited%20for%20alerts.%20I%20also%20utilized%20Thrifty%20Traveler's%20premium%20flight%20service%2C%20which%20sends%20flight%20deals%20to%20your%20inbox.%20When%20I%20saw%20the%20flight%20prices%20drop%20from%20MSP%20to%20Sydney%2C%20I%20dropped%20everything%20to%20check%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20could%20have%20transferred%20the%20points%20to%20an%20airline%20to%20get%20even%20more%20miles%20per%20point%20redemption%2C%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20long%20the%20flight%20deal%20would%20last.%20Thus%2C%20I%20booked%20directly%20through%20the%20Chase%20Ultimate%20Rewards%20travel%20platform%20to%20snag%20the%20flight%20deal.%20The%20cheapest%20and%20fastest%20flights%20were%20through%20United%2C%20an%20airline%20I%20have%20not%20flown%20frequently%2C%20but%20we%20were%20willing%20to%20book%20for%20the%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20adjusted%20our%20travel%20dates%20by%20a%20few%20days%20to%20ensure%20we%20got%20the%20cheapest%20deal%20but%20were%20still%20able%20to%20book%20the%20tickets%20for%20a%20two-week%20period%20that%20coincides%20with%20our%20children's%20spring%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20tickets%20for%20%241%2C117%20each%20and%20used%20my%20combined%20total%20of%20nearly%20330%2C000%20points%20to%20book%20them.%20Since%20I%20did%20not%20have%20enough%20points%20to%20cover%20the%20entire%20cost%20of%20the%20flights%2C%20I%20paid%20the%20remaining%20balance%20in%20cash%2C%20which%20ended%20up%20being%20about%20%24348.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20had%20to%20pay%20an%20annual%20fee%20to%20open%20the%20Ink%20Business%20Cash%20credit%20card%2C%20it%20was%20still%20worth%20it.%20Even%20including%20the%20annual%20fee%2C%20this%20strategy%20saved%20us%20just%20over%20%244%2C027%20on%20these%20four%20flights%20to%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20know%20where%20to%20start%3F%20Consider%20a%20financial%20advisor.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20who%20serve%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%20been%20vetted%20by%20SmartAsset%20and%20is%20held%20to%20a%20fiduciary%20standard%20to%20act%20in%20your%20best%20interests.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Start%20your%20search%20now.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-book-trip-to-australia-just-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741602241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676afa9b9de00e389eb34eff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-book-trip-to-australia-just-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20wanted%20to%20take%20my%20family%20of%2