rcial-vehicle-industry-set-for-3-5-growth-in-fy26-says-icra-125031000625_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Capital%20expenditure%20in%20the%20CV%20industry%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20rise%20significantly%20to%20Rs%2058-60%20billion%20in%20FY25%20and%20FY26%2C%20up%20from%20Rs%2034%20billion%20in%20FY24%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Findia-s-commercial-vehicle-industry-set-for-3-5-growth-in-fy26-says-icra-125031000625_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SRK%20wins%20tax%20case%20as%20ITAT%20dismisses%20issues%20over%20RaOne%20earnings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741601978000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118842637%2Cimgsize-28972.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan-wins-major-tax-case-as-itat-dismisses-issues-over-raone-earnings%2Farticleshow%2F118842642.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F118842642.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBollywood%20actor%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20secured%20a%20significant%20legal%20win%20in%20a%20long-standing%20tax%20dispute%20over%20his%20earnings%20from%20the%202011%20film%20'Ra.One'.%20The%20Income%20Tax%20Appellate%20Tribunal%20ruled%20in%20his%20favor%2C%20dismissing%20the%20reassessment%20of%20his%202011-2012%20income%20by%20the%20tax%20department.%20The%20reassessment%20had%20lacked%20fresh%20material%20and%20exceeded%20the%20four-year%20statutory%20limit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan-wins-major-tax-case-as-itat-dismisses-issues-over-raone-earnings%2Farticleshow%2F118842642.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Pak's%20Absence%20At%20India's%20CT%20Win%20Shows%20How%20Different%20Their%20Stories%20Are%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20when%20India%20celebrated%20its%20record%20third%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20title%2C%20the%20official%20hosts%20of%20the%20tournament%20were%20not%20in%20anyone's%20consciousness.%20Barring%20their%20name%20being%20featured%20on%20the%20host%20broadcaster's%20logo%20on%20TV%20screens%2C%20Pakistan%20was%20absent.%20Incredibly%2C%20there%20was%20not%20a%20single%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20official%20at%20the%20trophy%20ceremony%2C%20which%20was%20also%20dominated%20by%20Indian%20officials.%20Out%20of%20the%20four%20gentlemen%20who%20were%20on%20the%20stage%20to%20give%20away%20the%20medals%2C%20winners'%20jackets%20and%20the%20trophy%2C%20three%20were%20Indian%2C%20including%20Jay%20Shah%2C%20who%20was%20of%20course%20there%20in%20his%20capacity%20as%20the%20current%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20President.%20Understandably%2C%20many%20voices%2C%20including%20former%20cricketer%20Shoaib%20Akhtar%2C%20have%20questioned%20the%20lack%20of%20Pakistani%20representation%20on%20that%20stage.%20After%20all%2C%20how%20can%20there%20be%20no%20representation%20of%20the%20official%20hosts%2C%20even%20if%20the%20final%20and%20the%20ceremony%20were%20in%20Dubai%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEmbarrassing%20Optics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20to%20that%20question%20is%20actually%20a%20ridiculously%20simple%20one.%20An%20ICC%20spokesperson%20has%20ended%20the%20controversy%20(though%20this%20also%20will%20be%20questioned)%2C%20saying%20that%20no%20PCB%20official%20was%20present%20in%20Dubai%20for%20the%20final.%20The%20PCB%20Chairman%2C%20Mohsin%20Naqvi%2C%20couldn't%20travel%20to%20Dubai%20because%20of%20pressing%20engagements%20in%20Pakistan%20(he%20is%20also%20the%20Pakistan%20Interior%20Minister)%2C%20and%20neither%20did%20any%20other%20board%20official.%20Only%20office-bearers%20can%20be%20on%20the%20stage%20for%20a%20trophy%20presentation.%20This%20situation%20ideally%20should%20have%20been%20avoided%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20fact%20that%20Pakistan%20were%20the%20official%20host%20of%20an%20ICC%20event%20after%2029%20years.%20After%20the%20team%20had%20a%20nightmare%20run%20and%20were%20eliminated%20without%20a%20single%20win%2C%20and%20despite%20all%20the%20hype%20and%20chatter%20over%20the%20hybrid%20model%20that%20saw%20India%20play%20all%20their%20matches%20in%20one%20venue%20(Dubai)%2C%20Pakistani%20officials%20(whoever%20could%20travel%20at%20least)%20should%20have%20attended%20the%20final%20of%20what%20was%2C%20for%20all%20intents%20and%20purposes%2C%20their%20own%20event.%20The%20optics%20were%20embarrassing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo%20Nations%2C%20Two%20Stories%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20this%20was%20just%20another%20reminder%20of%20the%20stark%20contrast%20in%20the%20overall%20fates%20of%20India%20and%20Pakistan%E2%80%94two%20countries%20that%20were%20born%20together%20but%20which%20travelled%20very%20different%20paths%2C%20including%2C%20ultimately%2C%20on%20the%20cricket%20field.%20While%20the%20men%20in%20blue%20absolutely%20dominated%20the%20tournament%2C%20winning%20all%20five%20of%20the%20matches%20they%20played%20and%20successfully%20clinching%20a%20trophy%20they%20had%20last%20won%20in%202013%2C%20Pakistan's%20brand%20of%20cricket%20was%20not%20even%20a%20whisper%20on%20anyone's%20lips.%20As%20the%20Indian%20team%20celebrated%20on%20the%20victory%20podium%2C%2015%20men%20proudly%20wearing%20the%20white%20champion's%20jackets%20and%20celebrating%20their%20second%20ICC%20title%20in%20just%20over%20eight%20months%2C%20Pakistan%20was%20just%20missing%20in%20every%20which%20way%E2%80%94as%20hosts%20and%20as%20competitors.%20India%20not%20just%20reclaimed%20the%20trophy%20but%20the%20silverware%20essentially%20changed%20hands%20%E2%80%93%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20who%20were%20the%20defending%20champions%2C%20to%20a%20team%20which%20had%20been%20second-best%20to%20them%20the%20last%20time%20a%20Champions%20Trophy%20final%20was%20played%2C%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOff%20the%20field%2C%20though%20the%20PCB%20is%20assured%20of%20getting%20a%20hefty%20sum%20as%20hosting%20fees%2C%20along%20with%20a%20cut%20of%20the%20on-ground%20sponsorship%20and%20ticket%20revenue%2C%20there%20are%20some%20very%20big%20areas%20of%20concern.%20They%20reportedly%20spent%20around%20PKR%2012.8%20billion%20on%20stadium%20renovation%2C%20along%20with%20other%20expenses%2C%20and%20then%20witnessed%20venues%20that%20were%20not%20packed%20to%20the%20rafters%2C%20with%20multiple%20stands%20remaining%20vacant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20getting%20to%20host%20all%20matches%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20including%20the%20final%2C%20would%20have%20hurt%20too.%20But%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20this%20was%2C%20realistically%2C%20the%20only%20way%20a%20successful%20tournament%20could%20be%20held.%20Pakistan's%20ultimate%20fate%20in%20the%20tournament%20was%20also%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20overall%20fate%20of%20the%20two%20countries.%20In%20the%20almost%2078%20years%20since%20independence%2C%20India%20has%20established%20itself%20as%20an%20Asian%20superpower%20and%20a%20global%20player%2C%20while%20Pakistan%20is%20still%20riddled%20with%20internal%20conflict%20with%20a%20reported%20external%20debt%20of%20over%20%24130%20billion.%20Ironically%2C%20the%20ODI%20cricket%20field%20is%20one%20platform%20where%20Pakistan%20are%20still%20ahead%20of%20India%2C%20having%20dominated%20head-to-head%20proceedings%20in%20the%201980s%20and%20%E2%80%9890s%2C%20but%20there's%20no%20denying%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20scales%20have%20tilted%2C%20in%20this%20millennium%2C%20almost%20completely%20India's%20way.%20The%20two%20teams%20played%20bilateral%20ODI%20cricket%20last%20in%202012-13%2C%20when%20Pakistan%20travelled%20to%20India%20and%20lost%20a%20three-match%20series%201-2.%20Now%2C%20they%20only%20clash%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20and%20ICC%20events.%20Though%20Pakistan%20did%20beat%20India%20by%20a%20huge%20margin%20of%20180%20runs%20in%20the%202017%20Champions%20Trophy%20final%2C%20India%20have%20been%20the%20stand-out%20team%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20winning%2013%20of%2017%20ODIs%20against%20the%20men%20in%20green%20since%202010.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Wide%20Gulf%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20'80s%20and%20'90s%2C%20many%20of%20Pakistan's%20big%20wins%20against%20India%20in%20this%20format%20were%20registered%20in%20the%20UAE%20and%20in%20Sharjah%2C%20specifically.%20In%20fact%2C%20going%20into%20their%20clash%20this%20time%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20Dubai%2C%20Pakistan%20boasted%20a%20head-to-head%20record%20of%2019%20wins%20in%2028%20ODIs%20against%20India%20in%20the%20UAE%20and%20also%20a%20T20i%20win%20at%20the%20same%20venue%20in%20the%202021%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20But%20the%20result%2C%20with%20India%20winning%20more%20than%20comfortably%20by%20six%20wickets%2C%20with%2045%20deliveries%20remaining%2C%20highlighted%20just%20how%20big%20the%20gulf%20is%20between%20these%20two%20countries%2C%20on%20the%20cricket%20field%20too.%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20went%20on%20record%20to%20say%20that%20Pakistan%20would%20struggle%20against%20even%20a%20second-string%20Indian%20team.%20Former%20Pakistan%20cricketer%20and%20one%20of%20the%20best%20all-rounders%20in%20limited%20overs%20cricket%20history%2C%20Shahid%20Afridi%2C%20summed%20up%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20when%20he%20told%20the%20host%20broadcasters%20that%20India%20just%20has%20more%20match-winners%20than%20Pakistan%2C%20going%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20match-winner%20is%20someone%20who%20knows%20how%20to%20win%20the%20game%20single-handedly.%20Right%20now%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20such%20players%20in%20Pakistan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Stellar%20Performance%20By%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20quick%20overview%20of%20India's%20performance%20at%20the%20%E2%80%98mini-World%20Cup'%20this%20time%20will%20show%20that%20the%20team%20was%20not%20really%20stretched%20to%20the%20limit%20by%20any%20other%20team%20in%20the%20competition.%20While%20India%20once%20again%20stamped%20their%20authority%20as%20the%20best%20team%20in%20Asia%20by%20miles%2C%20dealing%20with%20Bangladesh%20and%20Pakistan%20with%20ease%2C%20they%20were%20also%20not%20overtly%20challenged%20as%20such%20by%20either%20Australia%20or%20New%20Zealand.%20Despite%20how%20high%20your%20heart%20rate%20might%20have%20been%20in%20the%20summit%20clash%2C%20when%20India%20needed%2040%20off%2036%20balls%20to%20win%2C%20with%20five%20wickets%20in%20hand%2C%20those%20who%20track%20Indian%20cricket%20knew%20that%20the%20batters%20in%20the%20middle%20would%20just%20deconstruct%20the%20situation%20into%20a%20T20%20match%20to%20stave%20off%20pressure%2C%20shaving%20off%20roughly%2010%20deliveries.%20So%2C%20in%20the%20mind%20of%20a%20current%20Indian%20batter%2C%20the%20same%20equation%20is%20actually%2040%20needed%20off%2026%20balls.%20India%20ultimately%20won%20the%20final%20with%20a%20full%20over%20to%20spare.%20There's%20no%20doubt%20that%20there%20was%20pressure%2C%20like%20KL%20Rahul%20admitted%20after%20the%20match%2C%20but%20this%20team%20knows%20all%20too%20well%20how%20to%20handle%20match%20tension.%20India%20at%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20this%20time%20were%20not%20just%20clinical%2C%20they%20also%20gave%20the%20world%20another%20reminder%20of%20just%20how%20dominant%20a%20limited-overs%20side%20they%20have%20become.%20In%20the%20last%20three%20men's%20ICC%20tournaments%20(ODIs%20%26amp%3B%20T20is%20combined)%2C%20India%20triumphed%20in%2023%20of%2024%20completed%20matches.%20The%20only%20match%20they%20lost%20was%20the%20final%20of%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20India%20won%20the%202013%20Champions%20Trophy%20title%2C%20the%20highlight%20of%20the%20trophy%20celebrations%20were%20Virat%20Kohli's%20Gangnam-style%20dance%20moves%20and%20push-ups.%20Though%20we%20didn't%20see%20any%20similar%20moves%20this%20time%2C%20the%20first%20ICC%20ODI%20title%20in%20twelve%20years%20for%20the%20number-one%20ranked%20ODI%20team%20in%20the%20world%20was%20another%20strong%20message%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20cricketing%20world.%20Team%20India%20is%20what%20the%20mighty%20Aussies%20were%20once%20to%20world%20cricket.%20Pakistan%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20still%20scrambling.%20The%20two%20completed%20matches%20they%20played%20this%20time%20saw%20them%20lose%20by%20substantial%20margins%20of%2060%20runs%20and%20six%20wickets.%20The%20second%20one%20was%20against%20India%20in%20Dubai%E2%80%94once%20Pakistan's%20own%20home%20base.%20In%20the%20last%2020%20completed%20ODIs%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20men%20in%20blue%20have%20won%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20India%20Needed%20This%20Win%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Indian%20team%20and%20the%20management%20know%20just%20how%20dominant%20a%20side%20they%20have%20become%20in%20limited-overs%20cricket%2C%20this%20title%20win%20was%20something%20they%20really%20needed.%20After%20failing%20to%20cross%20the%20final%20hurdle%20at%20the%20last%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20and%20that%20too%20at%20home%2C%20the%20low%20of%20losing%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%20a%20bilateral%20series%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2027%20years%20last%20year%20and%20then%20not%20managing%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20ICC%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20only%20salve%20that%20could%20heal%20those%20wounds%2C%20at%20least%20to%20a%20certain%20extent%2C%20was%20an%20ICC%20trophy.%20The%20other%20expectation%20before%20this%20tournament%20was%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%20playing%20characteristic%20stellar%20knocks%2C%20which%20had%20been%20missing%20from%20their%20repertoire%20for%20some%20time.%20Suffice%20it%20to%20say%2C%20no%20critic%20will%20be%20asking%20when%20these%20two%20stalwarts%20are%20going%20to%20hang%20up%20their%20boots%2C%20any%20time%20soon.%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20has%20his%20first%20big%20title%20as%20India%20coach%20and%20will%20also%20be%20breathing%20a%20lot%20easier%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECredit%20where%20credit%20is%20due%3A%20by%20and%20large%2C%20no%20one%20can%20find%20fault%20with%20any%20of%20India's%20strategies%20at%20this%20tournament.%20Playing%20five%20spinners%20ultimately%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20masterstroke.%20It%20was%20fitting%20that%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%2C%20one%20of%20India's%20all-time%20best%20all-rounders%20and%20yet%20a%20largely%20underrated%20player%2C%20because%20of%20his%20position%20in%20the%20batting%20order%2C%20hit%20the%20winning%20runs%20in%20the%20final.%20ODIs%2C%20which%20had%20suddenly%20become%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20problem%20area%2C%20are%20once%20again%20a%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20priceless%20treasure%20is%20the%20incredible%20squad%20and%20team%20depth%20that%20gave%20the%20Indian%20team%20their%20aura%20of%20invincibility.%20The%20title%20win%20was%20a%20complete%20team%20effort%2C%20with%20almost%20every%20player%20who%20took%20the%20field%20through%20the%20tournament%20stepping%20up%20to%20the%20plate%20to%20deliver.%20The%20middle%20and%20lower%20orders%E2%80%94once%20India's%20Achilles%20heel%E2%80%94are%20now%20the%20most%20dependable%20in%20world%20cricket.%20With%20the%20likes%20of%20Shubman%2C%20KL%2C%20Shreyas%2C%20Hardik%2C%20Varun%2C%20Axar%2C%20Kuldeep%20and%20others%20as%20the%20flag-bearers%20of%20the%20future%2C%20with%20Virat%2C%20Rohit%20and%20Jadeja%20as%20mentors%20and%20with%20the%20T20i%20team%20dominating%20every%20opposition%2C%20the%20fate%20of%20Indian%20limited%20overs%20cricket%20overall%20is%20definitely%20in%20great%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Long%2C%20Lightless%20Tunnel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20can't%20be%20said%20about%20Pakistan%20cricket.%20Former%20captain%20Babar%20Azam%20and%20current%20ODI%20skipper%20Mohammad%20Rizwan%20were%20axed%20from%20the%20T20i%20team%20for%20the%20upcoming%20series%20vs%20New%20Zealand%2C%20in%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20Pakistan's%20early%20ouster%20from%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%3B%20a%20new%20captain%20was%20named.%20Another%20example%20of%20the%20situation%20Pakistan%20cricket%20finds%20itself%20in%20as%20it%20desperately%20tries%20to%20find%20some%20light%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20very%20long%20tunnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20only%20similarity%20between%20the%20Indian%20and%20Pakistan%20cricket%20teams%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20always%20find%20themselves%20in%20the%20same%20group%20at%20a%20multi-nation%20tournament%20because%20a%20clash%20of%20the%20arch-rivals%20is%20still%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20cricketing%20cash%20cow%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20contest%20is%20now%2C%20almost%20completely%2C%20a%20one-sided%20affair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20former%20sports%20editor%20and%20primetime%20sports%20news%20anchor.%20He%20is%20currently%20a%20columnist%2C%20features%20writer%20and%20stage%20actor)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741601880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F7ibt43sg_team-india-afp_625x300_09_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fchampions-trophy-why-pakistans-absence-at-indias-win-was-disgraceful-7890770%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20was%20just%20another%20reminder%20of%20the%20stark%20contrast%20in%20the%20overall%20fates%20of%20India%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20two%20countries%20that%20we