rs%20and%20community%20partners%20in%20Austin%20to%20refine%20its%20technology%2C%20and%20added%20that%20Waymo%20engages%20proactively%20with%20local%20law%20enforcement%20and%20community%20groups%20in%20all%20the%20areas%20it%20operates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWaymo's%20safety%20data%20is%20available%20to%20the%20public.%20Over%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20fully%20autonomous%20miles%20traveled%2C%20the%20record%20shows%20that%20the%20Waymo%20Driver%20is%20making%20roads%20safer%20where%20we%20operate%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdam%20Greenfield%2C%20director%20of%20advocacy%20at%20road%20safety%20group%20Safe%20Streets%20Austin%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20while%20self-driving%20cars%20show%20promise%20in%20cutting%20deaths%20from%20drunken%20driving%20and%20reckless%20driving%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20regulation%20in%20Texas%20was%20concerning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20be%20very%20careful%20in%20thinking%20through%20the%20possible%20ramifications%20of%20this%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20Greenfield%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20society%20have%20a%20pretty%20consistent%20track%20record%20of%20letting%20technology%20wash%20over%20us%2C%20and%20then%20trying%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20consequences%20later%20when%20we're%20very%20much%20on%20the%20back%20foot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-tesla-battle-in-austin-robotaxi-wars%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741600867000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c7420eb8b41a9673f9a204%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-tesla-battle-in-austin-robotaxi-wars%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Waymo%20and%20Tesla%20robotaxis%20are%20set%20to%20battle%20it%20out%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20Austin%2C%20America's%20new%20robotaxi%20capital.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tcarter%