20to%20be%20a%20bad%20reference%2C%20don't%20put%20them%20down%20as%20a%20reference%E2%80%94that's%20just%2C%20in%20red%20words%2C%20stupid.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you're%20a%20recruiter%20with%20job%20interview%20tips%20you'd%20like%20to%20share%2C%20please%20contact%20this%20editor%2C%20Manseen%20Logan%2C%20at%20mlogan%40businessinsider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-hired-after-leaving-job-on-bad-terms-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741597621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b936c87a3d27148875e02a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-hired-after-leaving-job-on-bad-terms-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Google%20recruiter%20Nolan%20Church%20said%20it's%20best%20to%20mend%20bad%20relationships%20when%20leaving%20a%20job%2C%20but%20if%20that's%20not%20possible%20show%20self-awareness.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Alyshia%20Hull)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A172%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-hired-after-leaving-job-on-bad-terms-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prince%20William%20is%20frustrated%20over%20Meghan%20for%20THIS%20reason%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741597593000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118839746%2Cimgsize-52512.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fprince-william-is-frustrated-over-meghan-markles-alleged-attempt-to-channel-princess-diana-report%2Farticleshow%2F118839588.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F1