-pill-what-to-know-about-self-managed-abortions-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emisoprostol%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fabortion-pill-women-stockpile-mifepristone-trump-presidency-experts-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emifepristone%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20two%20pills%20commonly%20used%20to%20induce%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-abortion-decision-final-ruling-scotus-roe-v-wade-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabortions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20law%20reclassified%20the%20drugs%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-drug-scheduling-system-heroin-marijuana-2016-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtrolled%20substances%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20designation%20typically%20given%20to%20medications%20that%20carry%20the%20risk%20of%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBamboo%20Health%2C%20the%20company%20running%20Louisiana's%20prescription%20monitoring%20database%2C%20is%20ready%20to%20track%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcvs-walgreens-to-sell-abortion-pills-contested-by-scotus-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrugs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20March%2C%20Louisiana%20clinicians%20are%20required%20to%20log%20every%20mifepristone%20and%20misoprostol%20prescription%20they%20write%20in%20Bamboo's%20database%2C%20according%20to%20the%20New%20Orleans%20Health%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20former%20Bamboo%20employee%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Bamboo%20announced%20its%20intention%20to%20monitor%20the%20drugs%20in%20an%20internal%20Slack%20channel%20last%20year%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20the%20company's%20legal%20obligation%20as%20Louisiana's%20prescription-monitoring%20vendor.%20The%20employee%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20discussing%20sensitive%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETexas%2C%20Indiana%2C%20and%20Idaho%20are%20considering%20similar%20measures%20for%20tracking%20these%20drugs.%20All%20three%20states%20work%20with%20Bamboo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBamboo%20Health%20CEO%20Jeff%20Smith%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20company's%20prescription%20monitoring%20platform%20must%20comply%20with%20state%20regulations.%20%26quot%3BThey%20determine%20how%20that%20data%20is%20managed%20and%20accessed.%20That's%20how%20it%20gets%20treated%20in%20Louisiana%20and%20anywhere%20else%20it%20would%20occur%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMisoprostol%20isn't%20just%20for%20abortions.%20It's%20also%20used%20to%20treat%20stomach%20ulcers%2C%20manage%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fmiscarriage-rates-by-week%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emiscarriages%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20stop%20excessive%20bleeding%20after%20childbirth%2C%20a%20leading%20cause%20of%20death%20for%20women%20on%20delivery%20day.%20With%20a%20controlled-substance%20designation%2C%20misoprostol's%20routine%20use%20faces%20restrictions%20and%20state%20scrutiny%2C%20with%20potentially%20negative%20consequences%20for%20patient%20care%2C%20according%20to%20multiple%20physicians%20and%20public%20health%20officials%20who%20spoke%20with%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELouisiana%20has%20required%20some%20manual%20reporting%20of%20these%20drugs%20since%20October%2C%20according%20to%20a%20lawyer%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20state's%20guidance.%20With%20Bamboo's%20electronic%20system%20rolled%20out%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctors-chief-medical-officers-healthcare-google-uber-salesforce-executives-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoctors%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20concerned%20about%20who%20will%20be%20able%20to%20access%20the%20data%20and%20what%20they'll%20use%20it%20for%2C%20said%20Dr.%20Jennifer%20Avegno%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20New%20Orleans%20Health%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgovernment-tracking-drug-prescriptions-2015-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrescription%20monitoring%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20PMPs%2C%20are%20routinely%20used%20to%20investigate%20doctors%20for%20wrongdoing.%20Crackdowns%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopioid-overdoses-in-the-us-are-surging-with-the-pandemic-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopioid%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%20reduced%20prescriptions%2C%20but%20sometimes%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20much-needed%20care%20as%20doctors%20worried%20about%20being%20prosecuted%20for%20doing%20their%20jobs.%20Some%20experts%20worry%20reproductive%20medicine%20could%20share%20the%20same%20fate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERep.%20Jolanda%20Jones%20of%20the%20Texas%20House%20of%20Representatives%2C%20who%20sits%20on%20the%20House's%20public%20health%20committee%2C%20said%20she's%20concerned%20clinicians%20will%20hold%20back%20in%20prescribing%20mifepristone%20and%20misoprostol%20where%20medically%20necessary%20%E2%80%94%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftexas-abortion-maternal-health-desert-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleave%20their%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20state%20entirely%20%E2%80%94%20if%20they're%20afraid%20of%20being%20jailed%20for%20providing%20adequate%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20were%20a%20doctor%2C%20I'd%20be%20thinking%2C%20now%20I've%20got%20Big%20Brother%20looking%20into%20how%20I'm%20practicing%20medicine%3F%20Why%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20have%20a%20chilling%20effect%20on%20medical%20care.%20We're%20already%20seeing%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abortion%20pills%20in%20bottles%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0mifepristone%20and%20misoprostol%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c9f6ec585f1dff88b16451%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222790%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3Emifepristone%20and%20misoprostol%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FCharlie%20Neibergall%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20government%20started%20funding%20states%20to%20set%20up%20PMPs%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20in%20response%20to%20the%20prescription%20opioid%20crisis.%20Most%20states%20now%20require%20doctors%20to%20check%20them%20before%20writing%20certain%20kinds%20of%20prescriptions.%20If%20a%20search%20shows%20that%20a%20patient%20is%20getting%20opioids%20from%20a%20laundry%20list%20of%20emergency%20rooms%2C%20that%20could%20be%20a%20sign%20that%20he's%20%26quot%3Bdoctor-shopping%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20misleading%20physicians%20for%20pills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20safeguard%20came%20with%20tradeoffs%3A%20If%20you've%20had%20a%20prescription%20for%20a%20controlled%20substance%20in%20your%20life%2C%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20can%20view%20it%20in%20your%20state%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrivate%20health%20information%20is%20usually%20protected%20under%20the%20Health%20Insurance%20Portability%20and%20Accountability%20Act.%20But%20when%20controlled%20substance%20prescriptions%20are%20reported%20to%20the%20state%2C%20they%20lose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fwhat-is-hipaa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHIPAA%3C%2Fa%3E%20protections.%20Without%20those%20safeguards%2C%20third%20parties%20can%20access%20the%20data%20without%20patient%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPMP%20access%20can%20extend%20to%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20groups%2C%20including%20state%20licensing%20boards%20and%20health%20departments%2C%20parole%20and%20probation%20agencies%2C%20and%20medical%20examiners%20and%20coroners.%20Under%20various%20conditions%2C%20law%20enforcement%20can%20also%20access%20the%20prescription%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20of%20drugs%20that%20PMPs%20monitor%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20details%20they%20collect%2C%20has%20steadily%20grown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20earliest%20PMPs%20collected%20limited%20patient%20information%2C%20and%20only%20about%20prescriptions%20with%20the%20highest%20risks%20of%20misuse%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffda-chief-approved-oxycontin-six-figure-gig-at-purdue-pharma-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoxycodone%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-fentanyl-crisis-mexico-canada-harm-reduction-expert-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efentanyl%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%202024%2C%20however%2C%2045%20states%20monitor%20all%20controlled%20substances%2C%20and%2037%20track%20%26quot%3Bdrugs%20of%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20prescriptions%20that%20are%20not%20heavily%20regulated%20that%20the%20state%20deems%20risky%20for%20some%20individuals%2C%20according%20to%20research%20by%20health%20and%20law%20policy%20expert%20Jennifer%20Oliva.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20collected%20for%20each%20prescription%20is%20extensive%3A%20the%20drug's%20name%2C%20strength%2C%20quantity%2C%20and%20dispense%20date%3B%20the%20doctor's%20and%20pharmacist's%20DEA%20registration%20numbers%3B%20along%20with%20the%20patient's%20name%2C%20address%2C%20ZIP%20code%2C%20gender%2C%20date%20of%20birth%2C%20and%20driver's%20license.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222622%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20New%20York%20woman%20holds%20up%20a%20%23End%20Overdose%20blue%20sign%20at%20an%20International%20Overdose%20Awareness%20Day%20protest%20in%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ca063eb8b41a9673f9eac9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221967%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20International%20Overdose%20Awareness%20Day%20protest%20in%20New%20York%20in%202023.%20All%2050%20states%20have%20electronic%20PMPs%2C%20introduced%20largely%20to%20reduce%20overdoses%20from%20prescription%20opioids.%3Cp%3EErik%20McGregor%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EManaging%20this%20growing%20mountain%20of%20sensitive%20prescription%20data%20became%20a%20big%20business%20for%20Bamboo%20Health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBamboo%20was%20founded%20as%20Appriss%20in%201994%20in%20Louisville%2C%20Kentucky.%20Its%20first%20product%20was%20a%20data-aggregation%20and%20notification%20tool%20that%20informed%20victims%20when%20their%20offenders%20were%20released%20from%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tool%20became%20a%20%2430%20million%20business%20serving%2048%20states.%20The%20company's%20subsequent%20products%20helped%20law%20enforcement%20track%20sex%20offenders%20and%20monitor%20people%20who%20bought%20high%20quantities%20of%20Sudafed%20at%20pharmacies%2C%20which%20cops%20used%20to%20bust%20meth%20labs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20opioid%20crisis%20came%20to%20a%20head%2C%20Appriss%20was%20well-suited%20for%20the%20job.%20With%20its%20data%20prowess%20and%20close%20relationships%20with%20state%20governments%20%E2%80%94%20plus%20an%20early%20partnership%20with%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Boards%20of%20Pharmacy%2C%20which%20advises%20state%20PMP%20decision-makers%20%E2%80%94%20the%20company%20gobbled%20up%20PMP%20contracts%20and%20cemented%20a%20dominant%20position%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBamboo%20Health%20is%20now%20an%20independent%20company%20separated%20from%20other%20business%20lines%20built%20long%20ago%20under%20the%20Appriss%20name.%20Smith%2C%20the%20CEO%2C%20said%20Bamboo%20works%20with%2044%20US%20states%20and%20territories%20to%20facilitate%20more%20than%207%20billion%20prescription%20queries%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20PMPs%20earn%20money%20directly%20from%20states%20and%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20hospitals%20themselves.%20Bamboo's%20PMP%20business%20makes%20up%20roughly%20half%20the%20company's%20revenue%2C%20according%20to%20a%20former%20employee%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter.%20Altogether%2C%20Bamboo%20Health%20is%20bringing%20in%20more%20than%20%24100%20million%20annually%2C%20per%20a%20February%20LinkedIn%20post%20by%20its%20recently%20departed%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20commercial%20revenue.%20Smith%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20company's%20financials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20business%20has%20attracted%20large%20investors.%20Private%20equity%20firms%20Insight%20Partners%20and%20Clearlake%20Capital%20have%20backed%20Bamboo%20and%20sit%20on%20its%20board%20of%20directors%2C%20according%20to%20federal%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Appriss%20rebranded%20to%20Bamboo%20Health%20after%20buying%20PatientPing%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20collects%20data%20about%20patient%20admissions%2C%20discharges%2C%20and%20transfers%2C%20for%20about%20%24500%20million.%20The%20deal%20valued%20the%20combined%20company%20at%20more%20than%20%241.5%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vision%2C%20as%20Bamboo%20described%20it%2C%20was%20to%20combine%20the%20two%20companies'%20vast%20data%20feeds%20to%20equip%20providers%20with%20all%20the%20information%20they%20need%20during%20crucial%20moments%20of%20patient%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20several%20years%2C%20PMPs%20have%20assisted%20regulators%20in%20busting%20pill-mill%20networks%20and%20curbing%20severe%20prescribing%20patterns.%20Bamboo%20even%20helped%20the%20feds%20hold%20pharmaceutical%20distributors%20accountable%20for%20their%20role%20in%20the%20opioid%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it's%20not%20clear%20that%20PMPs%20have%20reduced%20patient%20harm%20overall.%20One%20study%20showed%20that%20tools%20such%20as%20PMPs%20might%20increase%20heroin-related%20deaths%20as%20prescription%20opioid%20abusers%20switch%20to%20illicit%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWired%20reported%20in%202021%20that%20a%20key%20Bamboo%20product%2C%20which%20displayed%20%26quot%3Boverdose%20risk%20scores%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20a%20patient's%20prescription%20history%2C%20was%20sometimes%20used%20to%20deny%20patients%20needed%20healthcare.%20Pharmacies%2C%20hospitals%2C%20and%20doctor's%20offices%20turned%20patients%20with%20high%20scores%20away%2C%20even%20when%20they%20had%20good%20reasons%20for%20taking%20opioids%2C%20such%20as%20endometriosis%2C%20a%20painful%2C%20chronic%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20former%20employees%20told%20BI%20that%20after%20the%20criticism%2C%20Bamboo%20prioritized%20updating%20the%20design%20of%20the%20scores%20to%20add%20more%20context%20and%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20point%20isn't%20to%20be%20the%20arbiter%20on%20who%20this%20person%20is%20and%20what%20they%20should%20get%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20ex-staffers%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20to%20equip%20somebody%20with%20some%20information%20to%20make%20a%20better%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221962%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22appriss%20ceo%20mike%20davis%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c9f75f585f1dff88b16466%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221472%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMike%20Davis%20cofounded%20Appriss%2C%20now%20Bamboo%20Health%2C%20and%20served%20as%20its%20CEO%20until%202020.%3Cp%3EAppriss%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBamboo's%20newest%20directive%20to%20monitor%20abortion%20medications%20may%20test%20this%20hands-off%20approach.%20Some%20employees%20worry%20that%20tracking%20these%20drugs%20will%20harm%20doctors%20and%20patients%2C%20rather%20than%20advancing%20the%20company's%20goal%20of%20improving%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProviding%20monitoring%20of%20mifepristone%20and%20misoprostol%2C%20in%20support%20of%20limiting%20the%20use%20of%20and%20access%20to%20those%20drugs%2C%20is%20acting%20in%20direct%20contradiction%20of%20that%20mission%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20former%20employee%20who%20was%20working%20at%20Bamboo%20when%20the%20company%20internally%20announced%20plans%20to%20monitor%20the%20drugs.%20The%20person%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20because%20they%20were%20not%20authorized%20by%20Bamboo%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20dangerous%20thing%20when%20a%20healthcare%20company%20is%20not%20making%20decisions%20based%20on%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20the%20patient%2C%20but%20on%2C%20perhaps%2C%20opportunities%20for%20near-term%20revenue%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20employee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20how%20Bamboo%20has%20responded%20to%20employee%20pushback%20about%20the%20company%20monitoring%20abortion%20pill%20prescriptions%20in%20Louisiana%2C%20Smith%20said%20as%20Bamboo%20has%20expanded%20its%20focus%20to%20patients%20with%20high-need%20conditions%20in%20areas%20like%20behavioral%20health%2C%20it's%20sought%20out%20new%20employees%20with%20expertise%20in%20those%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20important%20that%20we%20have%20the%20right%20people%20on%20the%20team%20to%20help%20us%20execute%20on%20that%20vision%20and%20mission%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNot%20everybody's%20going%20to%20be%20on%20the%20same%20page%2C%20as%20we%20look%20to%20expand%20our%20charter%20and%20where%20we're%20going.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20states%20have%20aggressively%20enforced%20abortion%20bans%2C%20putting%20new%20pressure%20on%20some%20doctors.%20Texas%20and%20Louisiana%20have%20sued%20and%20indicted%20at%20least%20one%20doctor%20for%20prescribing%20abortion%20pills%20to%20state%20residents%20via%20telehealth%20services.%20Idaho%20and%20Texas%20let%20private%20citizens%20sue%20virtually%20anyone%20who%20performs%20or%20assists%20with%20an%20abortion.%20These%20so-called%20bounty-hunter%20laws%20award%20%2410%2C000%20or%20more%20to%20successful%20plaintiffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Trump%20administration%2C%20states%20will%20be%20even%20more%20emboldened%20to%20use%20all%20the%20tools%20at%20their%20disposal%20to%20restrict%20access%2C%20Randi%20Seigel%2C%20a%20lawyer%20specializing%20in%20healthcare%20at%20the%20firm%20Manatt%2C%20Phelps%20%26amp%3B%20Phillips%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPregnant%20individuals%20in%20Louisiana%20are%20not%20subject%20to%20criminal%20prosecution%20for%20obtaining%20and%20using%20these%20drugs%20for%20self-managed%20abortions.%20But%20the%20doctors%20and%20pharmacists%20involved%20are%20another%20story.%20In%20these%20cases%2C%20somebody%20who's%20suspicious%20about%20why%20a%20patient%20was%20given%20mifepristone%20could%20report%20it%20to%20law%20enforcement%20and%20trigger%20an%20investigation.%20Officials%20could%20then%20seek%20access%20to%20PMP%20data%20for%20that%20investigation%2C%20per%20Seigel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbortion%20regulations%20are%20already%20getting%20in%20the%20way%20of%20necessary%20medical%20care%3A%20Several%20women%20have%20died%20from%20preventable%20complications%20after%20they%20couldn't%20access%20timely%20treatment%20in%20states%20with%20abortion%20bans%2C%20ProPublica%20has%20reported.%20Although%20certain%20legal%20exceptions%20are%20supposed%20to%20protect%20the%20life%20of%20the%20mother%2C%20some%20doctors%20may%20wait%20too%20long%20to%20intervene%20out%20of%20fear%20that%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eif%20the%20patient%20isn't%20clearly%20dying%2C%20their%20use%20of%20the%20drugs%20could%20be%20questioned%2C%20Seigel%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20concerned%20that%20tracking%20misoprostol%20and%20mifepristone%20prescriptions%20could%20have%20a%20similar%20effect%20on%20doctors'%20decisions.%20If%20doctors%20are%20concerned%20they%20may%20be%20accused%20of%20triggering%20an%20abortion%20while%20providing%20legal%20and%20medically%20necessary%20services%2C%20they%20might%20delay%20giving%20that%20care%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20could%20imagine%20somebody%20coming%20in%20who's%20having%20a%20miscarriage%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20is%20appropriate%20for%20miscarriage%20management%20%E2%80%94%20and%20somebody%20saying%2C%20'Well%2C%20wait%2C%20we%20have%20to%20wait%20a%20little%20longer%20to%20make%20sure%20you%20are%20really%20having%20a%20miscarriage%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Louisiana%2C%20which%20has%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20maternal%20mortality%20rates%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20new%20regulations%20are%20already%20causing%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faspiring-obgyns-worried-about-adequate-training-post-roe-v-wade-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eobstetrician-gynecologists%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20carried%20misoprostol%20in%20their%20pockets%20for%20emergencies.%20Now%2C%20the%20medicine%20must%20be%20stored%20in%20locked%20cabinets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAvegno%20told%20BI%20that%20clinicians%20across%20Louisiana%20have%20been%20running%20%26quot%3Btime%20trials%26quot%3B%20to%20test%20how%20quickly%20they%20can%20retrieve%20misoprostol%20from%20those%20locked%20cabinets%2C%20bring%20it%20back%20to%20the%20patient%2C%20and%20administer%20it.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20severe%20postpartum%20hemorrhaging%2C%20mere%20minutes%20could%20be%20the%20difference%20between%20life%20and%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222830%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Louisiana%20governor%20Jeff%20Landry%20signed%20the%20first%20bill%20of%20its%20kind%20to%20make%20mifepristone%20and%20misoprostol%20controlled%20substances%20in%20May%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ca05edb8b41a9673f9eaab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222123%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELouisiana%20Gov.%20Jeff%20Landry%20signed%20the%20state's%20law%2C%20the%20first%20of%20its%20kind%2C%20to%20make%20mifepristone%20and%20misoprostol%20controlled%20substances%20in%20May%202024.%3Cp%3EChris%20Maddaloni%2FCQ%20Roll%20Call%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20outpatient%20pharmacies%20have%20decided%20to%20stop%20stocking%20the%20pills%20altogether%2C%20Avegno%20added.%20Others%20are%20going%20beyond%20what's%20required%20by%20the%20law%2C%20including%20calling%20doctors%20to%20confirm%20what%20they've%20written%20on%20the%20prescriptions%2C%20slowing%20down%20access%20for%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20pharmacists%20are%20often%20confused%20about%20the%20law%20and%20afraid%20of%20liability%2C%20Avegno%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20fill%20this%20prescription%20and%20somebody%20uses%20it%20to%20secretly%20have%20an%20abortion%2C%20am%20I%20going%20to%20be%20held%20liable%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20introduction%20of%20mifepristone%20and%20misoprostol%20monitoring%20via%20Bamboo's%20database%20could%20add%20to%20that%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20say%20I'm%20an%20OB.%20I%20have%20a%20busy%20clinic.%20I'm%20putting%20in%20IUDs%20all%20the%20time%2C%20I'm%20managing%20miscarriages%2C%20and%20I'm%20doing%20hysteroscopies%2C%20all%20of%20which%20might%20require%20me%20to%20write%20misoprostol%20prescriptions.%20And%20that's%20now%20going%20to%20be%20tracked%20in%20the%20PMP%2C%26quot%3B%20Avegno%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20is%20somebody%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20look%20at%20my%20list%20and%20say%2C%20'Oh%20my%20gosh%2C%20Jen%20Avegno%20wrote%2020%20prescriptions%20last%20month%3F%20That's%20too%20many.%20Let's%20investigate%20her.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20tip%20about%20Bamboo%20Health%20that%20you%20want%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20Rebecca%20Torrence%20(%2B1%20423-987-0320)%20using%20the%20encrypted%20app%20Signal.%20Here%20are%20other%20tips%20on%20how%20to%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Esafely%20communicate%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20with%20Business%20Insider%20reporters.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fabortion-meds-prescription-tracking-misoprostol-mifepristone-bamboo-health-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741597262000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b796a1eb4be2fff9a52aa6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fabortion-meds-prescription-tracking-misoprostol-mifepristone-bamboo-health-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Louisiana%20has%20started%20monitoring%20abortion%20pills.%20Some%20other%20states%20are%20likely%20to%20follow%20suit.%20It%20could%20have%20disastrous%20consequences%20for%20patients.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bdodge%40businessinsider.com%20(Blake%20Dodge%2CRebecca%20Torrence)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fabortion-meds-prescription-tracking-misoprostol-mifepristone-bamboo-health-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranya%20Rao's%20Alleged%20Political%20Links%20And%20A%20BJP-Congress%20Blame%20Game%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20Ranya%20Rao%20was%20arrested%20at%20Bengaluru%20airport%20for%20gold%20smuggling%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20actor%20approached%20two%20ministers%20in%20the%20Siddaramaiah-led%20Congress%20government%20to%20wriggle%20out%20of%20trouble.%C2%A0State%20BJP%20chief%20BY%20Vijayendra%20has%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bblatant%20violation%26quot%3B%20of%20protocols%20that%20allegedly%20enabled%20Ranya%20Rao%20to%20smuggle%20gold%20%26quot%3Bcould%20not%20have%20happened%20without%20the%20direct%20support%20of%20influential%20figures%20within%20the%20government%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20put%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20dock%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20alleged%20that%20under%20the%20Basavaraj%20Bommai-led%20BJP%20government%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20Industrial%20Area%20Development%20Board%20allotted%20land%20to%20Ranya%20Rao%20in%202023%20to%20set%20up%20a%20steel%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Tried%20To%20Contact%202%20Ministers'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20row%20over%20the%20actor's%20political%20connections%2C%20BJP%20leader%20and%20MLA%20Y%20Bharath%20Shetty%20told%20the%20media%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20she%20was%20caught%2C%20she%20tried%20to%20contact%20some%20Congress%20ministers%20to%20use%20their%20influence%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20problem.%20Now%20it%20is%20almost%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20that%20two%20ministers%20are%20trying%20to%20help%20her.%20The%20CBI%20has%20taken%20over%20the%20case%2C%20something%20solid%20will%20come%20out%20of%20it%20and%20we%20will%20know%20who%20is%20behind%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20BJP%20president%20Vijayendra%20cited%20media%20reports%20alleging%20the%20involvement%20of%20a%20prominent%20minister%20in%20the%20matter.%20In%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20he%20said%20the%20reports%20are%20not%20surprising%20%26quot%3Bgiven%20this%20government's%20track%20record%20of%20churning%20out%20scandals%20in%20increasingly%20'innovative'%20ways%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMedia%20reports%20about%20the%20involvement%20of%20a%20prominent%20minister%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsiddaramaiah%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40siddaramaiah%3C%2Fa%3E's%20government%20in%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20gold%20heists%20in%20recent%20times%20come%20as%20no%20surprise%E2%80%94especially%20given%20this%20government's%20track%20record%20of%20churning%20out%20scandals%20in%20increasingly%20%26quot%3Binnovative%26quot%3B%20ways!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20blatant%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Vijayendra%20Yediyurappa%20(%40BYVijayendra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBYVijayendra%2Fstatus%2F1898986511376228761%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2010%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20blatant%20violation%20of%20government%20protocols%20that%20allegedly%20enabled%20Ranya%20Rao%20to%20smuggle%20gold%20worth%20over%20Rs%2012%20crore%20-%20and%20possibly%20much%20more%20in%20the%20past%20-%20could%20not%20have%20happened%20without%20the%20direct%20support%20of%20influential%20figures%20within%20the%20government.%20If%20these%20reports%20are%20true%2C%20it%20raises%20serious%20questions%20about%20how%20deep%20this%20nexus%20runs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20state%20BJP%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20%40siddaramaiah%20would%20have%20received%20intelligence%20reports%20pinpointing%20the%20suspected%20ministers%20and%20their%20involvement.%20Any%20attempt%20by%20the%20government%20to%20shield%20those%20responsible%20will%20only%20backfire%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20CBI%20now%20stepping%20in.%20The%20truth%20will%20come%20out%2C%20and%20any%20cover-up%20will%20only%20further%20expose%20the%20government's%20complicity%20in%20this%20grievous%20offence%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Vijayendra%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20Kannada%20saying%20goes%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20cat%20may%20think%20the%20world%20won't%20notice%20if%20it%20drinks%20milk%20with%20its%20eyes%20closed%26quot%3B%20-%20but%20%40inckarnataka%20government%20must%20not%20fall%20into%20such%20an%20illusion!%20The%20people%20are%20watching%2C%20and%20justice%20must%20be%20served%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKarnataka%20Home%20Minister's%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20questions%20on%20BY%20Vijayendra's%20allegations%20that%20Ranya%20Rao%20contacted%20two%20state%20ministers%20after%20she%20was%20caught%2C%20state%20Home%20Minister%20G%20Parameshwara%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%20this%20has%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20CBI.%20Let%20the%20CBI%20come%20out%20with%20their%20findings.%20Till%20then%2C%20this%20is%20speculation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20land%20allotment%20to%20the%20actor%20during%20the%20BJP%20regime%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEven%20that%20has%20to%20be%20found%20out.%20I%20was%20told%20this%20was%20allotted%20when%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20power.%20Let%20them%20(CBI)%20find%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20is%20now%20investigating%20the%20sensational%20case%20that%20came%20to%20light%20after%20a%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)%20team%20stopped%20Ranya%20Rao%20at%20the%20Bengaluru%20airport%20last%20week%20and%20recovered%20gold%20bars%20weighing%2014%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDRI%20has%20said%20in%20court%20that%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20concerning%20national%20security.%20The%20CBI%20has%20now%20joined%20the%20probe.%20Ranya%20Rao%2C%20who%20is%20the%20stepdaughter%20of%20senior%20IPS%20officer%20K%20Ramachandra%20Rao%2C%20is%20currently%20in%20DRI's%20custody%20and%20is%20being%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Ranya%20Rao%20Was%20Caught%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanya%20Rao%20was%20one%20step%20away%20from%20clearing%20airport%20security%20at%20Bengaluru%20airport%20when%20a%20DRI%20team%20intercepted%20her%20and%20recovered%20the%20gold%20bars.%20The%2033-year-old%20actor%2C%20who%20started%20her%20career%20with%202014%20Kannada%20film%20Maanikya%2C%20had%20flown%20in%20from%20Dubai%20on%20an%20Emirates%20flight%20last%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BUpon%20examination%2C%20gold%20bars%20weighing%2014.2%20kg%20were%20found%20ingeniously%20concealed%20on%20person.%20The%20contraband%2C%20valued%20at%20Rs%2012.56%20crore%20was%20seized%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Customs%20Act%2C%201962%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20DRI%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20then%20moved%20to%20her%20home%20on%20Bengaluru's%20Lavelle%20Road%20and%20the%20investigators%20found%20more%20there.%20%26quot%3BFollowing%20the%20interception%2C%20DRI%20officers%20conducted%20a%20search%20at%20her%20residential%20premises%20located%20at%20Lavelle%20Road%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20where%20she%20resides%20with%20her%20husband.%20The%20search%20resulted%20in%20the%20seizure%20of%20gold%20jewelry%20worth%20Rs.%202.06%20crore%20and%20Indian%20currency%20amounting%20to%20Rs.%202.67%20crore%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DRI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Immigration%20department%20categorised%20Ranya%20Rao%20as%20a%20frequent%20traveller%20to%20foreign%20countries.%20On%20December%2024%20last%20year%2C%20she%20went%20to%20Dubai%20and%20returned%20to%20Bengaluru%20on%20December%2027.%20She%20visited%20the%20US%20on%20January%2018%20and%20returned%20on%20January%2025.%20Between%20February%202%20and%20March%203%2C%20Ranya%20Rao%20visited%20Dubai%20five%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20frequent%20overseas%20travel%20sparked%20suspicion%20and%20put%20her%20on%20the%20authorities'%20radar.%20She%20made%20as%20many%20as%2027%20trips%20to%20Dubai%20last%20year%20and%20this%20brought%20her%20under%20the%20DRI's%20lens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741597260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F0ebp7ffg_ranya-rao_625x300_05_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Franya-rao-gold-smuggling-case-ranya-raos-political-links-under-lens-and-a-bjp-congress-blame-game-7890197%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Days%20after%20Ranya%20Rao%20was%20arrested%20at%20Bengaluru%20airport%20for%20gold%20smuggling%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20actor%20approached%20two%20ministers%20in%20the%20Siddaramaiah-led%20Congress%20government%20to%20wriggle%20out%20of%20trouble.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Franya-rao-gold-smuggling-case-ranya-raos-political-links-under-lens-and-a-bjp-congress-blame-game-7890197%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20simple%20guide%20to%20Canada's%20federal%20election%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741597205000%2C%22visual%