2%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20an%20interesting%20question%20to%20try%20to%20answer%20for%20an%20intern%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20really%20know%2C%20because%20of%20course%20the%20actual%20answer%20is%20dependent%20on%20that%20person%20and%20their%20life.%20So%20I%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20articulate%20the%20framework%20I%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Emmett%20Shear%20(%40eshear)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Feshear%2Fstatus%2F1898576024331505904%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%209%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20pursue%20careers%20for%20different%20reasons%2C%20such%20as%20money%2C%20prestige%2C%20power%2C%20and%20advancement%20opportunities%2C%20Shear%20wrote.%20But%20there%20were%20downsides%20to%20each%20of%20these%20reasons%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoney%20is%20a%20top%20reason%2C%20Shear%20wrote%2C%20but%20has%20%26quot%3Bdiminishing%20returns.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrestige%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bmostly%20a%20trap%2C%20for%20the%20same%20reason%20designer%20clothing%20brands%20are%20bad%20deals%2C%26quot%3B%20Shear%20said.%20While%20a%20prestigious%20job%20%26quot%3Bmight%20make%20some%20less%20discerning%20people%20think%20better%20of%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20will%20not%20%26quot%3Bactually%20make%20you%20better%20or%20better%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShear%20added%20that%20jobs%20promising%20power%20only%20offer%20you%20%26quot%3Bborrowed%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20especially%20if%20one%20has%20just%20begun%20their%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20if%20they're%20pitching%20you%20on%20power%20it's%20usually%20a%20trick%20of%20some%20kind.%20They're%20trying%20to%20convince%20you%20to%20accept%20less%20compensation%20in%20other%20ways%20by%20offering%20a%20mirage%2C%26quot%3B%