e%20but%20also%20align%20with%20an%20ecological%20consciousness%20by%20reducing%20reliance%20on%20palm%20oil%20and%20maida%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%E2%80%99s%20bakery%20now%20churns%20out%20150%20kg%20of%20cookies%20daily%2C%20delighting%20up%20to%2015%2C000%20customers%20monthly.%20He%20is%20joined%20by%20his%20younger%20brother%20Dr%20Sumit%20Soni%2C%20a%20physiotherapist%20by%20profession%2C%20in%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20passion%20for%20creativity%2C%20Sumit%20became%20involved%20in%20designing%20innovative%20bakery%20and%20health-conscious%20food%20items.%20%E2%80%9COur%20offerings%20include%20millet%20cakes%20and%20cookies%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20flavours%2C%20such%20as%20vanilla%2C%20blueberry%2C%20chocolate%2C%20cumin%2C%20dry%20fruits%2C%20and%20more.%20We%20emphasise%20the%20use%20of%20multi-grains%20in%20our%20products%20and%20ensure%20they%20are%20free%20from%20adulteration.%20As%20my%20brother%20often%20says%2C%20our%20secret%20ingredient%20is%20love%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20joining%20his%20brother%20in%20the%20business%2C%20Sumit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20brother%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20helping%20me%20achieve%20my%20dreams%2C%20including%20supporting%20my%20education%20and%20career%2C%20and%20even%20the%20smallest%20of%20my%20desires.%20Through%20this%20family%20business%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20honour%20our%20bond%20and%20find%20joy%20in%20advancing%20our%20family%20name%20together.%20There%20is%20no%20greater%20happiness%20for%20me%20than%20this%20shared%20endeavour%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20these%20millet%20cookies%20and%20the%20burgeoning%20line%20of%20cakes%20have%20earned%20Amit%20an%20annual%20revenue%20of%20Rs%201.5%20crore%2C%20expanding%20his%20reach%20into%20cities%20like%20Bengaluru%20and%20Mumbai.%20He%20even%20plans%20to%20expand%20to%20overseas%20markets%20in%20Ethiopia%2C%20Germany%2C%20and%20Georgia.%3C%2