0internship%2C%20I%20received%20a%20pre-placement%20offer.%20In%202023%2C%20I%20officially%20joined%20Amazon%20with%20a%20CTC%20of%20around%2046%20LPA%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20Before%20joining%20Amazon%2C%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20mentor%2C%20taking%20technical%20sessions%20for%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20dreams%20into%20careers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20true%20impact%20of%20CybageKhushboo%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20success%20of%20its%20students.%20In%20the%20early%20years%2C%20only%2025%25%20of%20graduates%20were%20able%20to%20secure%20jobs%2C%20highlighting%20the%20challenges%20they%20faced%20beyond%20academics.%20Recognising%20this%2C%20the%20team%20expanded%20its%20focus%20in%202014%E2%80%94going%20beyond%20scholarships%20to%20equip%20students%20with%20essential%20soft%20skills%2C%20confidence-building%20exercises%2C%20and%20interview%20preparation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20have%20been%20remarkable.%20Today%2C%20an%20impressive%2095%25%20of%20students%20land%20jobs%20at%20leading%20companies%20through%20campus%20placements%2C%20proving%20that%20the%20right%20support%20can%20turn%20aspirations%20into%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20success%20story%20is%20that%20of%20Arjun%20Deshmukh%2C%20who%20secured%20a%20job%20at%20JP%20Morgan%20after%20graduation.%20%E2%80%9CArjun%20saved%20diligently%20over%20the%20years%2C%20and%20now%20he%20is%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley%2C%20pursuing%20his%20master%E2%80%99s.%20He%20started%20his%20course%20in%202023.%20My%20son%2C%20Anish%2C%20also%20studied%20at%20Berkeley%2C%20where%20he%20completed%20his%20degree%20in%20computer%20engineering.%20To%20be%20honest%2C%20I%20think%20I%20was%20even%20happier%20when%20Arjun%20received%20his%20admission%20to%20Berkeley%20than%20when%20Anish%20did%20in%202017.%20I%20was%20absolutely%20on%20top%20of%20the%20world%20when%20he%20told%20me%20he%20is%20going%20to%20Berkeley%2