layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUndeterred%20by%20this%20setback%2C%20he%20eventually%20found%20his%20true%20calling%20in%20the%20field%20of%20aquaculture.%20His%20growing%20interest%20led%20him%20to%20earn%20a%20Master%E2%80%99s%20in%20Aquaculture%20Management%20from%20the%20prestigious%20Central%20Institute%20of%20Fisheries%20Education%20(CIFE)%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fshrimp-farming-2-1740749226.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Manoj%20expanded%20his%20operations%20to%20400%20hectares%2C%20producing%20nearly%201%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20shrimp%20annually.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fshrimp-farming-2-1740749226.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fshrimp-farming-2-1740749226-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fshrimp-farming-2-1740749226-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fshrimp-farming-2-1740749226-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Fshrimp-farming-2-1740749226-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-410599%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20Dr%20Manoj%20expanded%20his%20operations%20to%20400%20hectares%2C%20producing%20nearly%201%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20shrimp%20annually.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201994%2C%20his%20life%20took%20a%20pivotal%20turn%20when%20Dr%20Manoj%20relocated%20to%20Olpad%2C%20Gujarat.%20It%20was%20here%20that%20he%20identified%20the%20untapped%20potential%20of%20shrimp%20farming%20in%20a%20state